      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>cheezy plant-based Mexican-Style pie </strong>with the <strong>green beans </strong>to the side</p><p>Tip: Drizzle over any remaining juices from the foil parcel!</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
